<br />

<br />
Most of us agree that the lag explanation was a very weak excuse, and far from the real reason(s).  Most likely the real reason was a combination of outcry from some influential non-bards at our _APPARENT_ imbalanced exp gain ability (which we know isn't really imbalanced, it's just particularly flashy), the prevalence of macro/autocircle aoe-ers, and the possibility of OoW pwnage with aoe (which remains to be seen).
<br />

<br />
